TopicTitle: Very low FPS on an ok PC

Articles.Content:

Cpu usage is not more than 30% on a single core in worst case scenarios

I5 2500k @ 4,6Ghz

16 GB DDR 3 1600Mhz

HD 7970 @ 1200 MHz core and 1500Mhz Mem

KSP is installed on a SSD

 

ty for the help in advance !
